		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You raise three magnetically charged pins aloft, and as they crash together they create a bolt of lightning that arcs toward your target. Upon striking, the lightning splits into multiple bolts that strike nearby foes.</em></p><p><strong>[[/save dexterity]]{Dexterity Save}</strong></p><p>Lightning bolts leap from your first target to up to three other targets within 30 feet of the first target. A target cannot be targeted by multiple bolts.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure: </strong>Target takes [[/damage]] damage.*</p></li><li><p><strong>Success: </strong>Half damage.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>*Upcasting:</strong> Increase damage by [[/damage 1d8 lightning]]{1d8} for each spell level above 6th.</p>",
